# Multiplayer Tic-Tac-Toe with Nakama — Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from plan. Last updated: 2026-04-09

## Active Technologies

- **Backend**: Go 1.26.1 — Nakama OSS runtime plugin (nakama-common v1.45.0)
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript 5.x — Vite 6 build
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4 + shadcn/ui
- **SDK**: @heroiclabs/nakama-js
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (Nakama-managed)
- **Auth**: Dual — Guest (device ID) + Registered (email/password, Google OAuth)
- **Testing**: go test (backend), Vitest + React Testing Library (frontend)
- **Deployment**: Docker Compose (DigitalOcean) + Vercel (frontend)

## Project Structure

```text
backend/
├── main.go              # InitModule — register handlers, create leaderboard
├── match_handler.go     # Match lifecycle handlers
